VulkanSceneGraph: VulkanSceneGraph (VSG), is a modern, cross platform, high performance
VulkanSceneGraph: scene graph library built upon Vulkan graphics/compute API. The
VulkanSceneGraph: software is written in C++17, and follows the CppCoreGuidelines and
VulkanSceneGraph: FOSS Best Practices. The source code is published under the MIT
VulkanSceneGraph: License, with the exception of vulkan.h, used for Vulkan extensions,
VulkanSceneGraph: which is under Apache License 2.0.
